# 显示COCO种类和超类
cats = coco.loadCats(coco.getCatIds())
nms=[cat['name'] for cat in cats]
print('COCO categories: \n{}\n'.format(' '.join(nms)))

nms = set([cat['supercategory'] for cat in cats])
print('COCO supercategories: \n{}'.format(' '.join(nms)))
